Game

Class Food

  • java.lang.Object
    • Game.Food
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Burrito, DryBiscuit, Grapes, JellyMeat, Lasagna, Salmon, Seed, SicknessCure, Soup, Steak, Tacos

    public abstract class Food
extends java.lang.Object
    The Food Class is for initializing Food objects and their attributes.

    Food is used to feed a pet. Different type of food exist therefore this class is needed to create multiple types of food. The Food class is also an abstract class.

    Author:
    Jade Martin, Kyran Stagg
